{"tid":975460,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《花樣年華》入選美國攝影學會（ASC）百大最佳攝影電影","createTime":"2019-01-09T15:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T15:34:03.000Z","uid":35221,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c1843021c84bd5a32131a95c359ea8b76556935b","tid":975460,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"原list:<br />\n<a href=\"https://theasc.com/news/asc-unveils-list-of-100-milestone-films-in-cinematography-of-the-20th-century\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheasc.com%2Fnews%2Fasc-unveils-list-of-100-milestone-films-in-cinematography-of-the-20th-century&d=4%2BvgcLjDEU85daVKvUDpCr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=5fc1ec2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://theasc.com/news/asc-unveils-list-of-100-milestone-films-in-cinematography-of-the-20th-century</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190109/_2019010921325129755.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190109%2F_2019010921325129755.jpg&h=0def26c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《花樣年華》是唯一一部入選百大的港產片。<br />\n<br />\n美國攝影學會（ASC）今年成立100周年紀念，近日ASC就由其會員投票，選出20世紀100部最佳攝影的電影。冠軍屬1962年的經典作品《沙漠梟雄》，由已故著名攝影師Freddie Young擔任拍攝。亞軍則是1982年作品《2020》，季軍位則是名作《現代啟示錄》。《大國民》及《教父》分別佔第4及5位。<br />\n<br />\n至於打入百大的亞洲電影並不多，包括張藝謀的《大紅燈籠高高掛》、日本已故名導黑澤明則有《羅生門》及《七俠四義》，而港產片只有王家衞執導的《花樣年華》打入百大，該片由杜可風及李屏賓擔任攝影。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1406757/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1406757%2F&d=4%2BvgcLjDEU85daVKvUDpCr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=3bff2876\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1406757%2F&h=5f15d4ce\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1406757/</a>"},{"pid":"cc940f3e545f47d3643c4722d5b43e64f3a0f396","tid":975460,"uid":206673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:53:26.000Z","msg":"真係要文藝片先做到"},{"pid":"8c4f0148a4292e4250a04c146e764be0922fc0db","tid":975460,"uid":183102,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:57:11.000Z","msg":"花樣年華真係每一個畫面都拍得勁靚，求其cap圖都靚到可以做wallpaper <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a459c95a8e05a30a16dbbaf843cb3399a272af7d","tid":975460,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T16:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d082ccec8d31772b582ffcf0e89ac90c33432c4a","tid":975460,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T09:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888f95ff4812a5424d914d5c54593f3fcfb86b81","tid":975460,"uid":175632,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T10:02:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0b389733da26c60b40b5dd4658162407699f11b","tid":975460,"uid":28181,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T10:05:38.000Z","msg":"又黎百大電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似年年都同一單新聞咁"},{"pid":"6d1b269e25566afca5696e83ccee4aa45da147c3","tid":975460,"uid":76143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T10:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c72ce3a22db5cb3300762f275e1016a2bcef05","tid":975460,"uid":27616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T10:13:01.000Z","msg":"2020<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"234d5d9ad0f6de3d355e0e400c7f35fa25d60590","tid":975460,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0b389733da26c60b40b5dd4658162407699f11b","tid":975460,"uid":28181,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T10:05:38.000Z","msg":"又黎百大電影<img src=\"/assets/f